description:
On my private Facebook Group of 6,000 .... hundreds of comments on the question, “Are you wearing a mask?” And precious little on my post sharing a LETTER you can send to your city council or state legislature asking them to “interpose” against your mayor or governor’s overreach that violates your constitutional rights.

I need ACTION TAKERS and LEADERS in there.

I want folks willing to question the media / govt narrative that has us all on house arrest.

It’s called: Supporting You In 2020 Crisis

See the link to join in Stories ☑️ #IDoNotConsent #FreedomOfSpeech #Cvd #cvd19
